# Implementation Plan — Phased Devnet & REST Backend Integration

This plan maps out the step-by-step phases to wire the deployed Solana Devnet program (`9AhsF4FXa6GPqVWJEaCdPeK3jptuGPfZpDk24Co5odsf`) to the React Native app using standard REST calls, and connect the backend.

---

## Architecture Flow (REST-Based)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────┐           HTTP GET
│        React Native App         │ ─────────────────────────────┐
│                                 │                              │
│ • Renders UI & Chart            │◄──────────────────────────┐  │
│ • Fetches pool details via REST │     JSON Pool Details     │  │
│ • Sends on-chain bets via MWA   │                           │  │
└────────────────┬────────────────┘                           │  │
                 │                                            │  │
